## Limitations

The report is based on available online resources and may not cover all social factors affecting the restaurant industry comprehensively. The data is limited to the information provided by the sources accessed, which may not reflect the most current trends or regional variations. Additionally, the analysis is constrained by the lack of specific data on individual restaurant groups, focusing instead on general industry trends.